### Get all todos
GET {{ez_todo_services_HostAddress}}/todo

###

### Create a todo
POST {{ez_todo_services_HostAddress}}/todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy groceries",
  "description": "Buy groceries for the week"
