Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy groceries",
  "description": "Buy groceries for the week"
}

###

### Toggle a todo
PATCH {{ez_todo_services_HostAddress}}/todo/1/toggle

###

### Delete a todo
DELETE {{ez_todo_services_HostAddress}}/todo/1

